10.What is OS?
Ans:Cascading medium between hardware and software.

11.Why linux not windows?
Ans:Free,open source,secure,Different distribution(ubuntu),Fast.

12.what is kernel?
Ans:It is heart of OS does device management
                          memory management
                          Process management
                          System handling

13.what is shell scripting?
Ans:Shell scripting is a text file with a list of commands to perform certain tasks.

